description.displayText: I first met Amylee 6 years ago when she joined my Girl Scout Troop in a Middle School.  Since that time I have continued to lead Amy's troop and watch her grow and mature into a smart, responsible young lady. Amy has a natural gentleness about her that makes her easy to approach and easy to talk to. I feel that Amy would be an asset to your organization.
